#: d2a601d0c26a4812a03db1259144cf50
msgid "Smart contract is not about replacing paper contract with electronic one, but replacing the Law with the transaction protocol. By doing so you're also replacing trust in justice by trust in the blockchain."
msgstr ""

#: ../../web3-dev/smart-contracts/introduction.rst:21
#: c79778db7484425a9d7dd7cd843510e8
msgid "In the following, and in the crypto ecosystem, we talk about smart contracts only to refer to a *program* that can be executed on a blockchain."
